<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">Each Petite Card was designed for that moment. Printed on soft, cotton paper that remembers the press of the letterform, they carry a quiet confidence — elegant but unpretentious, beautiful without trying too hard. They are the sort of cards that live in desk drawers beside good pens and secrets, ready for the next thank-you, congratulations, or confession.</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">Keep a six-pack and never be caught without a proper note again — or choose a single to accompany a gift, a gesture, or something that deserves its own envelope.</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p3"><b>Longbourn Papers. For the beautiful act of slowing down.</b><br></p>
